until we reach this dÃ©tente

00:06:47.209 --> 00:06:49.976
with the lining
of the uterus that we have.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:06:51.726
So we have this thick uterine lining

00:06:51.750 --> 00:06:53.934
and now it's got to come out,

00:06:53.958 --> 00:06:56.059
and how do you stop bleeding?

00:06:56.083 --> 00:06:58.476
Well, you stop a nose bleed
by pinching it,

00:06:58.500 --> 00:07:00.809
if you cut your leg,
you put pressure on it.